</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukenuon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kenuon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/6/01 7:14:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help me out with new legs =)</span><hr size=1> Gladiator Chain Leggings (no drop) are the legs to go. Looks are like banded on whatever race. Best stats imo.<br>
