other option of good legs are flayed paebala with 16 ac, 6 int, 20 hp/mana, and 20 svd.  they do drop off chetari, so you dont have to kill the goodly paebala for them.  they also have that heavy 20 svd bonus, which is a much neglected stat, and harb should be getting to the point they will be entering zland rotation soon.<br>
<br>
other options:<br>
giant scalemail 11ac 3int n3wis 20hp (for the wis loaded)<br>
carrion beetle 7ac 5agi 5svd 5svp<br>
<br>
also, cobalt drake hide leggings are ac9, 3cha, 25mana, 8svc.  there arent a whole lot of tailors on karana who are making the velious armors though, so they might cost you a bit or require you to provide a lot of cobalt drake pelts.  but these are a very viable option if you are looking for non no-drop druid legs. <p>-K<br>
